title: New PFE icon not showing up
body: I've had PFE for more than a year now and as Ezreal is my favorite champion, I really want an icon with him on it. The new icon hasn't shown up for me, though.

replies.body: Those new [**Pulsefire Ezreal icons**](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/page/pulsefire-caitlyn?utm_source=LeagueClient&utm_medium=OverviewTier2Pos1) will still be going out over the next week, but be sure to hit us up after 5/29 if you haven't goti t by then!
